{
  "stem": "1343.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyhow, it was a regular job from morning till evening for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One interesting story, but I have to go back for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was-- right after bar mitzvah, in Gyongyos I remember they were reading the Torah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after, you know, they finished, an old man, the shamash, was taking down the Torah, and there were four steps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he stumbled, fell, and the Torah fell out of his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And not only that, but the cover of the Torah, the cloth, was pulled off, and the Torah, naked, lay there on the floor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was a terrible tragedy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- --community, they divided 40 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Each had to fast for one day because of that fact.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So while I was in this camp, I became sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a cold and I developed a pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in the stable lying there in high fever, and the Germans were looking for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where is the little gardener, they called me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and they came into the stable and found me there, shivering and burning up with fever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they ordered the Hungarian soldiers to put me on a wagon and horse and buggy and took me in to a clinic.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I was waiting there in the clinic-- because there I had to wait until all the gentiles were taken care of, and at last I would be called in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While I was waiting there, a car pulled-- pulls up across the street, an open Mercedes, and some high-ranking German officers were getting off.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
